          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3395503-chad-harrison?shelf=historical-fiction">historical-fiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3395503-chad-harrison?shelf=religion">religion</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3317759619" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7627880785642084505">Other than some wooden dialogue and a surprisingly heavy focus on teenage romances, this is a good book. Entertaining and sweet. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


