<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/19798469-all-is-well"><img alt="All is Well (The Work and the Glory #9)" style="height: 75px;" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1462606793l/19798469._SY75_.jpg" />
